name: Blocks
description: Blocks (B) is a meme coin and digital collectible on the Stacks blockchain, created for entertainment only. It has no utility or promised value. It is led by the community and has the support of prominent long-time Stacks voices. The Blocks community is focused on expanding its presence on socials, web3 applications, and more. The future is unwritten on how Blocks will evolve. It is up to the community to decide the direction and next steps via authenticated voting processes.
